summary: Locate a mother's missing child in an abandoned mine.
descriptionHtml:
Fight your way through an abandoned mine to locate a mother's missing child.


This was created by a group of students working on their first questing mod. We created a unique level and quest for you to enjoy.  Any feedback is appreciated, as are any bugs you encounter.

Known issues- Spawn marker is in an incorrect location. Travel down the mountainside to locate the mine.  (FIXED 1.2)
author: Nathaniel Durfee - Cassandra Morgan - Jonathan Pruto - Evan Rockenbauch - Harrison Xu - Taylor Hess - Anthony Mezzapelle - Jason Schaufele - Anna Floyd - Drew Snyder
